metadata.name: Pepe Geeks Bar
metadata.description:
All Pepes are chilling at this special place right after beating up the evil with the power of friendship.

Starring: Naruto, Sasuke, Ash, Misty, Tanjiro, Nezuko, Erza Scarlet, Natsu Dragneel, Levi Ackerman, Mikasa Ackerman, Eren Jaeger, Usagi Tsukino, Rei Hino, L, Ryuk, Happy, Carla, Luffy, Nami, Sanji, Zoro, Pikachu, All Might, Saiki and Riki, Togepi, Baby Yoda, Kirby and Cheem.
